 59% ===== MODULE FUNCTIONS ========
 60
 61% Map Minimum and Maximum Input Processing Function
 62function y = mapminmax_apply(x,settings)
 63  y = bsxfun(@minus,x,settings.xoffset);
 64  y = bsxfun(@times,y,settings.gain);
 65  y = bsxfun(@plus,y,settings.ymin);
 66end
 67
 68% Competitive Soft Transfer Function
 69function a = softmax_apply(n,~)
 70  if isa(n,'gpuArray')
 71    a = iSoftmaxApplyGPU(n);
 72  else
 73    a = iSoftmaxApplyCPU(n);
 74  end
 75end
 76function a = iSoftmaxApplyCPU(n)
 77  nmax = max(n,[],1);
 78  n = bsxfun(@minus,n,nmax);
 79  numerator = exp(n);
 80  denominator = sum(numerator,1); 
 81  denominator(denominator == 0) = 1;
 82  a = bsxfun(@rdivide,numerator,denominator);
 83end
 84function a = iSoftmaxApplyGPU(n)
 85  nmax = max(n,[],1);
 86  numerator = arrayfun(@iSoftmaxApplyGPUHelper1,n,nmax);
 87  denominator = sum(numerator,1);
 88  a = arrayfun(@iSoftmaxApplyGPUHelper2,numerator,denominator);
 89end
 90function numerator = iSoftmaxApplyGPUHelper1(n,nmax)
 91  numerator = exp(n - nmax);
 92end
 93function a = iSoftmaxApplyGPUHelper2(numerator,denominator)
 94  if (denominator == 0)
 95    a = numerator;
 96  else
 97    a = numerator ./ denominator;
 98  end
 99end

100
101% Sigmoid Symmetric Transfer Function
102function a = tansig_apply(n,~)
103  a = 2 ./ (1 + exp(-2*n)) - 1;
104end
